{"id":3202,"date":"2023-07-25T15:58:19","date_gmt":"2023-07-25T08:58:19","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/?p=3202"},"modified":"2023-07-26T08:59:08","modified_gmt":"2023-07-26T01:59:08","slug":"nhung-hinh-anh-trong-buoi-thi-tocfl-ngay-23-7","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/nhung-hinh-anh-trong-buoi-thi-tocfl-ngay-23-7\/","title":{"rendered":"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh trong bu\u1ed5i thi TOCFL ng\u00e0y 23\/7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh Smart Way"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong>Bu\u1ed5i thi ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 TOCFL (Test of Chinese as a Foreign Language) ng\u00e0y 23\/7 v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i s\u1ee9c mong \u0111\u1ee3i, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m vinh d\u1ef1 l\u1edbn lao m\u00e0 Smart Way \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh d\u1ea5u m\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh du h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean.<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\">Smart Way xin ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u1ea3m \u01a1n s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n th\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 tham gia chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i thi TOCFL l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.\u00a0 Sau th\u1eddi gian h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp, \u00f4n luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9, kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ngh\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\">1 b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1t ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 TOCFL c\u1ea5p B1, m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1ea7m qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf trong h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\">9 b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u1eed th\u00e1ch v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 TOCFL c\u1ea5p A2, ch\u1ee9ng minh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng giao ti\u1ebfp c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft s\u00e2u h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\">3 b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean kh\u00e1c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 TOCFL c\u1ea5p A1, x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng t\u1eeb v\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 ng\u1eef ph\u00e1p c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n trong ti\u1ebfng Trung Qu\u1ed1c.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ngh\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean trong su\u1ed1t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Smart Way. B\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 \u0111am m\u00ea v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 chinh ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch TOCFL. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, c\u00f4ng ty Smart Way \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3, t\u1eadn t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t cho vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean. S\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eeb ph\u1ee5 huynh v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i xin ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng <a href=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/\">Smart Way<\/a> trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\">M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, ch\u00fac m\u1eebng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong k\u1ef3 thi TOCFL v\u1eeba qua. H\u00e3y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u1eef v\u1eefng tinh th\u1ea7n r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp, Smart Way t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 b\u1ea1n!<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3203\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/3.png\" alt=\"du-hoc-smart-way\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/3.png 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/3-300x169.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3204\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/4.png\" alt=\"du-hoc-smart-way\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/4.png 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/4-300x169.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3205\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/5.png\" alt=\"du-hoc-smart-way\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/5.png 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/5-300x169.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3206 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/6.png\" alt=\"du-hoc-smart-way\" wi